<collectingCountry id="81E81D961A31F469396A4EE2189DFDF8" box="[1151,1243,488,514]" name="Canada" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">Canada</collectingCountry>
south to South Carolina.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F9405D061A31F4693DD14D381EA7FD88" blockId="33.[151,1436,152,626]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">
<emphasis id="CB8B81141A31F4693DD14D381D2DFDB6" bold="true" box="[196,363,562,588]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">Larval hosts:</emphasis>
